Actualizar Sistema
sudo apt update && sudo apt dist-upgrade -y

Liberias
sudo apt install ffmpeg libavcodec-extra gstreamer1.0-libav gstreamer1.0-plugins-ugly gstreamer1.0-plugins-bad gstreamer1.0-pulseaudio vorbis-tools 
gdebi gdebi-core synaptic p7zip-full p7zip-rar rar unrar

Tipografias
sudo apt-get install fonts-freefont-ttf fonts-freefont-otf ttf-mscorefonts-installer fonts-ubuntu

Programas
sudo apt install cmatrix qbittorrent vlc fastfetch mousepad obs-studio kdenlive simplescreenrecorder ffmpeg eog -y

Porgramas y accesorios
sudo apt install

Install Flatpak
sudo apt install flatpak
flatpak remote-add --if-not-exists flathub https://dl.flathub.org/repo/flathub.flatpakrepo

